### 计算拉格朗日插值（3个点）
POST https://lagrange-interpolation.rbq.dev/api
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": [
    {
      "k": 0,
      "v": 1
    },
    {
      "k": 1,
      "v": 2
    },
    {
      "k": 2,
      "v": 4
    }
  ]
}

